,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"e26eac137e15a4fe44fe84a6d9835c64032ed401","tid":1295108,"uid":10402,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T08:24:51.000Z","msg":"掉返轉，要有大台/commander先做到，同大家理念差好遠。<br />\n而且大家improvise快過班死黑警調動，你見我地撚到狗嗰幾日好多時都係D死黑警先岩岩齊人守，我地臨時轉陣，咁樣佢地commander plan好左未來幾個鐘既戰術即刻無用。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T09:03:03.000Z","msg":"呢個可以用係小組上面，甚至係文宣、海外支援<br />\n或者近少少上次71掛黑旗就可以用得着呢個概念"},{"pid":"8f583f5d3b3bf858618848239168692b8cd5846f","tid":1295108,"uid":273297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T09:32:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"494cb9f44473cccebda67b1a260bc4fe9dbabbd6","tid":1295108,"uid":187493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T09:37:47.000Z","msg":"咁即係有大臺啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6de5401893e34803689e1033c706e8c5941f7e2","tid":1295108,"uid":118592,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"494cb9f44473cccebda67b1a260bc4fe9dbabbd6","tid":1295108,"uid":187493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T09:37:47.000Z","msg":"咁即係有大臺啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T09:39:00.000Z","msg":"各自爬山啦，但唔係onsite嗰啲內部計劃真係唔好亂比人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d02d6a31b862e7f919051b0e7d802cbc4b9292b0","tid":1295108,"uid":10402,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c6de5401893e34803689e1033c706e8c5941f7e2","tid":1295108,"uid":118592,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"494cb9f44473cccebda67b1a260bc4fe9dbabbd6","tid":1295108,"uid":187493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T09:37:47.000Z","msg":"咁即係有大臺啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T09:39:00.000Z","msg":"各自爬山啦，但唔係onsite嗰啲內部計劃真係唔好亂比人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T09:45:00.000Z","msg":"onsite嗰啲內部計劃點會有人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個就係即時improvise特性，琴日定前日掛黑旗都好似無咩人知有行動就掛左。咁樣幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}